### Hadith 4:35

*Narrated Anas bin Malik:*

When Allah's Apostle came to Medina, he ordered that a mosque be built.
He said, "O Bani An-Najjar! Suggest me a price for the garden of yours."
They replied, "By Allah, we will not ask its price except from Allah."

